column5: Has anyone been to Misaw lake lodge in Saskatchewan? If so, how was the fishing for large northerns? I am considering going there in 2002 and would like any info. thanks in advance for your help.Dana

I have heard Misaw is decent. I haven't been there myself yet. I have been to many others. How did you find out about them?For more options on northern Saskatchewan. www.4bigfish.com specializes in Northern Saskatchewan trophy fishing.Thanks, Mark
